sources.description:
RENFREW SAVES A LADY! The pride of the Mounties races to the rescue of a girl in distress!
Ann Fenwick witnesses a US bank robbery, gets kidnapped by the bandits, and is rescued by Renfrew of the Canadian Mounties and Kelly before being recaptured by the gang.

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/_HbTrvuN2l0


Original title: Fighting Mad (1939) 
This film is available with subtitles in many language options.

Director: Sam Newfield
Writers: George Rosener  John Rathmell 
Stars: James Newill, Sally Blane, Benny Rubin 
Genres: Colorized classics, Action, Adventure, Drama, Music
